{"tid":433203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多區下午高溫破33度　打破最接近年尾發酷熱警告紀錄","createTime":"2017-10-12T07:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T09:43:47.000Z","uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d46dcad345b9bbc1be6fa6fb238871256ffee2f1","tid":433203,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171012/s00001/9967e8dbfb395877e2ccbae9d1d79624.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171012%2Fs00001%2F9967e8dbfb395877e2ccbae9d1d79624.jpg&h=24ed9310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160210/photo/bkn-20160210053953857-0210_00862_001_09p.jpg?20160210060417\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160210053953857-0210_00862_001_09p.jpg%3F20160210060417&h=ccc4d995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中秋節已過，本港天氣仍然酷熱，今午多區氣溫升破33度。天文台在下午1時35分發出酷熱天氣警告，是自2000年設立警告以來，最接近年尾發出的一次。<br />\n<br />\n下午2時10分，天文台錄得氣溫32.2度，跑馬地、打鼓嶺、將軍澳、上水、石崗等地區升至超過33度，元朗及赤鱲角氣溫更超過34度。<br />\n<br />\n天文台預測本港下午天晴，天氣酷熱及乾燥，今晚漸轉多雲及有一兩陣雨，吹和緩東北風，今晚風勢清勁；展望未來一兩日早上較涼，星期日及星期一天氣轉壞，有狂風大雨。<br />\n<br />\n天文台本月3日亦曾發酷熱天氣警告，當時是警告首次在10月發出，維持6小時40分鐘，當日下午天文台在市區錄得氣溫達33.5度，是有紀錄以來10月第三高溫。<br />\n<br />\n除今年外，本港對上一次在10月錄得33度或以上高溫，已是1963年，當年10月錄得的最高氣溫為33.2度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins1710121507790155602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins1710121507790155602&d=zxSEwzIAsp08fc7Qcb1rKTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c556169e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins1710121507790155602&h=6779d723\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins1710121507790155602</a>"},{"pid":"ab0da8296113fc864cd697ac1ae30fce209f398e","tid":433203,"uid":57705,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:45:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09eee6e16961cd6d5234109839817d021967c94b","tid":433203,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n酷熱示意圖，睇完透心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0b32823f6bd0c275e2eb8e8445ed94c9b9e433","tid":433203,"uid":29887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:50:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"ff88268630c4ae4dc25f1d4e33a961216777ef1a","tid":433203,"uid":139247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:56:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"98ecbecb0b758987cf538a51dfab0f915581a8b6","tid":433203,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仆街死啦"},{"pid":"c94febb62ab4c01d7dc980681822721cd18fc617","tid":433203,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"正評是俾欣宜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec24789bf8f2a5e2f4d0686b4990f719c66b2045","tid":433203,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:26:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正評是俾欣宜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢位ching就識波喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5301fd12353b605db3f059bafdd7822caa55ecc8","tid":433203,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛放完假嗱？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zftap7wb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzftap7wb&h=aa56aa23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"055a5bfcf2042e1eafd439420ebc841254218bda","tid":433203,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e193f09b6399